diff --git a/docs/architecture.md b/docs/architecture.md
index aaaaaaa..bbbbbbb 100644
--- a/docs/architecture.md
+++ b/docs/architecture.md
@@ -22,6 +22,10 @@ The primary database runs PostgreSQL 15.4 on RDS.

 ### Database Architecture

-The application uses a single RDS PostgreSQL instance for all read/write operations.
+The application uses a primary RDS PostgreSQL instance for writes and an analytics
+read replica for heavy reporting queries. This offloads analytical workloads from
+the primary instance and allows independent scaling.
+
+The primary instance has been upgraded to db.r6g.2xlarge to handle increased write throughput.

